    <description>An expansion for Heroes of the Blitzkrieg.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Defeat, Defiance brings the British Expeditionary Force to the battlefield of France 1940. An expansion to the hugely popular Heroes of the Blitzkrieg, In Defeat, Defiance is the biggest British expansion ever. Included are over 170 counters, and fourteen intriguing scenarios.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The 170 counters include Vickers, Cruiser, and Matilda tanks, Bren carriers, 2pdr and 25mm Anti-tank guns, 51mm mortars, Leaders, heroes, snipers, Squads, Bren guns, Boys Anti-tank rifles, and much more. The fourteen scenarios, all designed by Dale Holmstrom (The Swift and the Bold) and Mark Walker, cover everything from British and SS fighting near Arras to Rommel crossing the Brasse Canal.&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game is no longer available and you can find the new, improved and expanded edition in Lock 'n Load Tactical: Heroes in Defiance&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
